  <CaptionedBlock heading="Free Training, Free Boarding and Real Aftercare" imagePosition="none" variant="card">
    <p>The price includes a free first lesson with an <a href="https://avs.nparks.gov.sg/outreach/resources/acdt-dog-trainers/" class="underline underline-offset-2 text-[var(--color-accent-hover)]">AVS-Accredited Certified Dog Trainer</a>, free boarding after your deposit until you're ready, and free ongoing customer service for care questions after the sale. For a Specified breed, that first lesson is worth its weight in gold.</p>
    <p>And the safety net we're asked about most: if your Shepherd falls sick within the first 5 days of going home, bring them back to the shop and we'll nurse them ourselves.</p>
    <div slot="side" class="clay h-full bg-[var(--color-mint-100)] p-6 sm:p-8">
